### ============================================================
### OAuth2 & JWT APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Google
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/google
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Kakao
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/kakao
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 로그인 URI 조회 - Apple
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/uri/apple
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Google (GET)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/google?code=auth-code-here&device_type=ANDROID&device_id=device-123
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Kakao (GET)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/kakao?code=auth-code-here&device_type=IOS&device_id=device-456
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### OAuth2 콜백 - Apple (POST with id_token)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/callback/apple?code=auth-code-here&id_token=apple-id-token&device_type=IOS&device_id=device-789
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 모바일 앱용 소셜 로그인 - Google
### (네이티브 SDK에서 받은 access_token을 직접 전달)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/mobile/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "provider": "google",
  "accessToken": "google-access-token-from-native-sdk",
  "deviceType": "ANDROID",
  "deviceId": "device-unique-id"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 모바일 앱용 소셜 로그인 - Kakao
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/oauth/mobile/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "provider": "kakao",
  "accessToken": "kakao-access-token-from-native-sdk",
  "deviceType": "IOS",
  "deviceId": "device-unique-id"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### JWT 토큰 갱신 (Reissue)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/reissue
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 로그아웃 (현재 세션)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 전체 로그아웃 (모든 세션)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/jwt/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 활성 세션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/jwt/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 토큰 상태 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/jwt/token-status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### Kakao Webhook APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카카오 연결 해제 웹훅 (Unlink Webhook) - GET
### 카카오에서 사용자가 앱 연결을 끊었을 때 호출됩니다.
### Authorization 헤더에 어드민 키가 필요합니다.
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/oauth/kakao/webhook/unlink?app_id=123456&user_id=987654321&referrer_type=UNLINK_FROM_APPS
Authorization: KakaoAK test-admin-key
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카카오 연결 해제 웹훅 (Unlink Webhook) - POST
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/oauth/kakao/webhook/unlink?app_id=123456&user_id=987654321&referrer_type=ACCOUNT_DELETE
Authorization: KakaoAK test-admin-key
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
